N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 4025.19 - Closing time-entries, declarations

State Regulations

Except in overnight races, if the hour for closing of
entries or for declarations is not stated, such hour shall be understood to be
midnight of the day specified. Notes
